## ğŸ§¼ Best Practices for Variable Naming

| Bad âŒ      | Better âœ…            |
| ----------- | -------------------- |
| `a = 50`    | `age = 50`           |
| `t = 98.6`  | `temperature = 98.6` |
| `n = "Ava"` | `name = "Ava"`       |

